  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the same time, in the ghetto I was involved with the illegal youth organization, the social democratic youth organization called And we used to come together in little groups having all kind of lectures, listening to even to music sometimes, having a seminar.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But these were small groups.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Reading illegal literature.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was, in a way, a little bit of an involvement which my mother, although she was not too much anxious for us to do this kind of work knowing that if German find out then death.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was no school at that time in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we, the young people, started to be involved in teaching the children in the so-called-- we called this the children corners where children who were not able to go to school-- the schools were closed-- we used to take them to ghetto to teach them songs, to teach them how to write and, in a way, giving them a little bit of life.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the houses there they were created house committees to help the starvation which started in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the ghetto, in the Warsaw ghetto itself, over 2,000 house committees were created by the Jews themselves, the so-called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Illegal Jewish cultural organization was created.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we, the young people, started to have seminars, I recall, that and later assigned to places to go after the curfew and to have lectures for the people of the houses which were closed up.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, a 16, 17-year-old, went to such lecture and I recall it was [INAUDIBLE] and I was talking about [INAUDIBLE], about [NON-ENGLISH] at this particular lecture.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
